Package arf.question

Class Summary
AbstractQuestion  
BooleanResult The Boolean result class represents the object which is returned by a Boolean question.
ConfigurationResult The configuration result class represents the object which is returned by a configuration question.
NumericResult The numeric result class represents the object which is returned by a numeric question.
QuestionHandle The question handle class encapsulates a question.
QuestionService This class is an abstract base class for questions of the adaptation reasoning framework.
QuestionTrader The question trader manages all questions of the framework.
StringResult The string result class represents the object which is returned by a string question.
UnknownResult The unknown result class represents the object which is returned if no reasoner is available or no question was found for a handle.
URIResult The resource result class represents the object which is returned by a configuration question.
